      <title>贝莱德（Blackrock）的Mazzocchi说，希望美联储举行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-19/expect-the-fed-to-hold-blackrock-s-mazzocchi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BlackRock EMEA Wealth Solutions共同贝蒂纳·马佐基（Bettina Mazzocchi）讨论了美国市场的业绩，并提出了周三晚些时候对美联储的政策决定的期望。她告诉彭博电视台：“市场将要看的是围绕美联储和另一家中央银行将要发表的陈述的叙述。” （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-19/expect-the-fed-to-hold-blackrock-s-mazzocchi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 09:02:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
